ieber, \u00dcbelkeit, Juckreiz, Durchfall, Nephrotoxizit\u00e4t, exfoliative Dermatitis und periphere Polyneuropathie. Bei der einmaligen, niedrigen Dosis Suramin, die die Kinder in der neuen Studie erhielten, traten aber au\u00dfer vor\u00fcbergehenden Hautausschl\u00e4gen keine Nebenwirkungen auf. ..", "language": null, "image": null, "pagetype": "website", "links": [null, "https://www.symptome.ch", "https://www.symptome.ch", null, "/whats-new/posts/", "/find-threads/unanswered", "/members/list/", null, "/forums/bewegung.99/", "/forums/entgiftung.447/", "/forums/ernaehrung.23/", "/forums/nahrungsergaenzung.241/", "/forums/saeure-basen-haushalt.167/", "/forums/gefuehlswelt.204/", "/forums/psyche-und-gesundheit.183/", "/forums/selbstfindung.432/", "/forums/staerkung-fuer-psyche-geist-und-seele.203/", "/forums/umgang-mit-stress.187/", "/forums/soziales-umfeld.323/", "/forums/familie-und-erziehung.264/", "/forums/leben-im-alter.443/", "/forums/partnerschaft-und-sexualitaet.260/", "/forums/erlebnisse.106/", "/forums/gemeinsam-vorwaerts.350/", "/forums/humor.31/", "/forums/kreativitaet.285/", "/forums/alltagstipps.185/", "/forums/buecher-gesundheit-leben.125/", "/forums/nachdenken.109/", "/forums/philosophie.184/", "/forums/religion.213/", null, "/forums/elektrosmog.22/", "/forums/geopathie.24/", "/forums/gifte.28/", "/forums/koerperpflege-kosmetik.407/", "/forums/radioaktivitaet.415/", "/forums/wohn-und-arbeitsumfeld.164/", "/forums/amalgam.3/", "/forums/bakterien-resistente-staemme.362/", "/forums/impfungen.178/", "/forums/medizinische-behandlungsfehler.440/", "/forums/zahnmedizin-und-zahnprobleme.191/", "/forums/alkohol.108/", "/forums/nikotin.101/", "/forums/rund-ums-thema-sucht.306/", "/forums/verschiedene-drogen.160/", null, "/krankheiten/", "/forums/ads-adhs-autismus.202/", "/forums/akne-ausschlag.462/", "/forums/allergie.166/", "/forums/asthma.467/", "/forums/augenkrankheiten.468/", "/forums/bakterielle-fehlbesiedlung.363/", "/forums/borreliose.150/", "/forums/b